--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CHANGES
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
        o
    ____|____
   |         |  This file lists changes made to the Ansible role.
   |  _   _  |  The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and
   | [_] [_] |  formatted to allow easy grepping by scripts.
   |____~____|
    ___//__//   The fields are:
   /|     |/    B: bug
  //|_____|     F: feature
    _|| ||_     I: improvement
   (__| |__)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.5.1 (2016-03-30)
B: Fix path parameter in remove task

* Version 0.5.0 (2016-02-26)
F: Add support for OS family 'OpenBSD'

* Version 0.4.0 (2016-01-21)
F: Drop support for OS family 'Gentoo'

* Version 0.3.5 (2015-11-17)
I: Add missing Ansible tags

* Version 0.3.4 (2015-11-08)
I: Improve 'group_vars' and 'host_vars' options

* Version 0.3.3 (2014-12-19)
I: Various small Ansible and Jinja2 improvements

* Version 0.3.2 (2014-10-15)
I: Update to version '1.8.11_p1' on Gentoo

* Version 0.3.1 (2014-09-11)
I: Change license from 'GPLv2' to 'Simplified BSD License'

* Version 0.3.0 (2014-08-24)
F: Add support for OS family 'FreeBSD'

* Version 0.2.0 (2014-08-14)
F: Remove support for OS family 'RedHat'

* Version 0.1.5 (2014-08-14)
I: Improve conditional statements

* Version 0.1.4 (2014-07-26)
I: Disable 'requiretty' to speed-up Ansible

* Version 0.1.3 (2014-07-22)
B: Remove 'recurse' argument from directory remove task

* Version 0.1.2 (2014-07-08)
B: Fix wrong variable name

* Version 0.1.1 (2014-07-06)
B: Add missing default variables

* Version 0.1.0 (2014-07-02)
F: Initial release
